whereas.text:
Whereas the Obama administration has stated that the 
          Authorization for Use of Military Force
			 Against Iraq Resolution of 2002 (
          Public Law 107–243

        ) is obsolete and has
			 supported its repeal;

Whereas the 
          Authorization for Use of Military Force (
          Public Law 107–40

        ) should not apply to ISIS
			 because ISIS has no operational connection to al Qaeda or the Taliban and
			 is not currently considered an associated force of al Qaeda;
